parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the front bumper can cause a road hazard, increasing the risk of a crash or injury for other road users.
symptoms: The front bumper falls off
the bumper is loose
the bumper is trapped underneath the vehicle
the vehicle vibrates
and an abnormal sound is heard coming from underneath the front end of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in recall repair can cause owners to continue driving vehicles with safety issues, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Owners receive notification of a recall but are unable to get the repair done due to parts not being available
dealerships not having a solution
or manufacturers not providing a timeline for repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The shattering of the sunroof can cause injury to occupants or distraction while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The sunroof shatters without impact
causing a loud noise and potentially injuring occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vibration of the driver side mirror can cause distraction while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The driver side mirror vibrates at varying speeds
making it difficult to focus on the image
and potentially causing the driver to lose attention on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lunge forward or fail to stop, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brakes feel like they slip or disengage
the vehicle lunges forward
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the vehicle shakes or vibrates when braking
the steering wheel vibrates when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Warped rotors can cause the vehicle to vibrate or shake when braking, leading to reduced braking performance and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates or shakes when braking
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lunge forward or fail to stop, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brakes feel like they slip or disengage
the vehicle lunges forward
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Lower Bumper Cover Assembly Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the front lower bumper cover assembly can create a road hazard, increasing the risk of a crash or injury for other road users.
symptoms: The front bumper cover assembly detaches from the vehicle
causing a road hazard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents or injuries to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly when pressing the brake
putting the driver and others at risk for injury.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood latch can cause the hood to open while driving, obstructing the driver's view and increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The hood is not sealing flush
causing a gap and allowing wind to catch while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vibration of the side mirrors can cause distractions while driving, increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The driver-side mirror shakes in its housing at varying speeds and on non-smooth roads
causing a distraction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause accidents or injuries to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The vehicle surges forward while applying maximum brake force
causing an unexpected jolt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting of the side mirrors can cause a distraction while driving, increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The side mirrors melt and deform
causing a distraction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The shattering of the sunroof/moonroof can cause injuries to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The sunroof/moonroof shatters while driving
causing glass to fall into the vehicle.
